> Thanks Matt.  That was very interesting.
>
> The main problem is that there are plenty of tires in the 205/75/R15 
> size
> but none that are LT rated.
>
[...]
>
>
> In a perfect world I would get 15"x5.5" rims and just run 215/75R15 LT
> tires.  But I do not know of a 15x5.5 aftermarket rim that looks like 
> the
> bus stock wheels.
>
> Good Luck,
> Adrian S. Pillow
